data.title: The Pragda Complete Film Collection
data.text:
An enlightening journey through our renowned collection that illuminates Spain and Latin America's rich tapestry. Explore over 50 important subjects that capture the essence of this vibrant region. More than 30 countries are represented in this collection of 500 films, all in their original language with English captions or subtitles.

New to Pragda? Please sign up and login to preview and/or license this collection. If your institution has already licensed this collection, you will need to access this page from your institution's network to watch the film. For help on using Pragda, please visit our help wiki.
